Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.91,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,FAMOUS DETECTIVE HOLMES
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.06,0:01:40.98,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Flight Championship of Chaos!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.88,0:01:43.97,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! It's finally complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.21,0:01:45.87,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Helen! Helen!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:57.55,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Come and see, Helen.\NQuickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.13,0:02:00.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! Is this it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.83,0:02:02.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared with the\Nearlier prototypes...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:04.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,this engine is several\Ntimes more powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:08.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:11.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I was beginning to worry that it\Nwouldn't be ready on time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:13.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. With this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:16.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll win this year's World Aircraft\NChampionship for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.91,0:02:20.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I will preserve the honour of England!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we celebrate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.51,0:02:47.20,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, we'll eat out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.66,0:03:03.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:11.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's grab it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.87,0:03:16.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:22.61,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:42.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Put out that fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.21,0:03:53.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use.\NIt's not going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.68,0:03:57.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,My precious cloak!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.88,0:03:59.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go out! Go out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:07.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my! Fire! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:09.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Rats! Hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:25.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And there goes another one.\NI wonder if it's close by?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.28,0:04:31.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Those flames appear to be quite high...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.78,0:04:38.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But a fire usually appears to be\Ncloser than it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:40.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That smoke isn't the type you would\Nexpect to see if a house was on fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:42.36,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be from a factory...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.36,0:04:44.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,or some place where the fire\Nis burning quantities of oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.06,0:04:46.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That direction...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:49.69,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,that would be the factory\Nowned by Mac Bain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.60,0:04:54.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mac Bain? Do you mean the famous\Naeronautical engineer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.20,0:04:56.97,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember right, he's the favourite\Nto win the world aircraft championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:59.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A race that will be held in Holland\Nsometime soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.77,0:05:02.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,My late husband really\Nadmired him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.91,0:05:04.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I do hope everything's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:06.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then.\NWhy don't we have a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:36.07,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How terrible! Where is Mac?\NIs Helen safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.68,0:05:38.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am, it's too dangerous!\NStay back! Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:40.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We are acquaintances of Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.68,0:05:42.91,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Sherlock Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.02,0:05:43.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:45.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay here, Mrs. Hudson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.05,0:06:14.60,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mac! Helen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:25.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:27.75,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How could this have happened\Nin an empty factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.93,0:06:37.37,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it. Someone must have\Nknocked this over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.67,0:06:39.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.91,0:06:41.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.24,0:06:44.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,My engine! I've just completed it!\NIt's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.38,0:06:48.35,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stay back, Mr. Mac Bain.\NIt's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:50.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,The engine was just completed?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It can't be.\NThe efforts of a lifetime have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:07:01.63,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,We understand how you feel.\NMac, please get a hold of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.04,0:07:16.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief, one of our fire trucks\Nhas disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible! Keep looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:31.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I made some hot soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.29,0:07:32.95,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have some,\Nit'll make you feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.73,0:07:35.85,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome to\Nstay here if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much for your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:41.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear, I don't think you should give\Nup just because the engine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:41.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.84,0:07:44.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no hope whatsoever.\NIt's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:46.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Your wife is correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's too early to give up, Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.04,0:07:51.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Spare me your empty\Nwords of comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:55.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I am giving you no such thing, sir.\NI am saying that I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.02,0:07:57.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you found a clue?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:02.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that? It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:05.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This was left at the scene of the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:08.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that this scrap of cloth is\Nfrom the cloak of Professor Moriarty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.96,0:08:11.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriarty?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:15.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,An odd little man who fancies\Nhimself a criminal genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:16.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So, he stole the engine...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.04,0:08:17.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:20.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please help them, Mr. Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.59,0:08:33.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:39.42,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What the devil is this?\NAn engine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.53,0:08:42.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would dare drop such\Na filthy old thing out of the sky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:46.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Moriarty's aircraft Pteranodon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.87,0:08:48.84,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he intentionally drop it on me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.33,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,After him! Give chase!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.55,0:09:07.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.70,0:09:16.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What a wonderful engine!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:19.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, there's no doubt that\NI will win the world championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:21.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that we couldn't win\Nwith the engine that the Professor built.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.77,0:09:24.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... well.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:26.90,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:43.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Out to sea?\NWhere are they heading?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.37,0:09:54.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,"The judging committee has approved\Nthe entry of a mysterious aviator..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:57.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mr. Black Eagle, who had been\Npetitioning for some time..."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.10,0:09:59.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,"to be allowed to participate\Nin the race."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.21,0:10:01.83,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious aviator?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.04,0:10:03.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this face!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:06.04,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Who else could this be\Nother than Moriarty?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:10.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He is going after the prize of\N100,000 crowns, Moriarty, that fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.35,0:10:12.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to win the championship\Nwith a stolen engine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:14.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,that's thoroughly unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:26.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Mac Bain was always\Nso kind to my late husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.50,0:10:28.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to do something\Nto help him in return.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:30.89,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You look very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.04,0:10:33.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise, I won't get in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:35.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,In any event, I've already decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.14,0:10:37.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:38.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.35,0:10:39.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.10,0:11:03.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.70,0:11:05.67,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get us to Holland!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:08.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I will capture Moriarty with\Nmy own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:16.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:32.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Holmes,\Nyour reputation precedes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.27,0:11:34.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to Holland.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.57,0:11:38.23,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,In terms of this Mr. Black Eagle,\Nwe've discussed whether we should...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.31,0:11:40.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,accept his entry or not. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.58,0:11:42.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,However?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.74,0:11:46.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you heard the old story\Nfrom medieval times?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:48.51,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Where a mysterious cavalier\Ncame out of nowhere to participate...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:50.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,in a joust and won the title?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:52.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that you accepted\Nthe mysterious pilot's entry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.42,0:11:53.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,in honour of that cavalier.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.05,0:11:55.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:58.56,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Moriarty used foul means to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.69,0:12:01.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have proof that\NMr. Black Eagle is Moriarty?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:02.79,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.93,0:12:04.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind the issue of proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.20,0:12:06.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I will never allow\Nhis wrongdoing to succeed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.47,0:12:11.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,- How do you see the outcome of this race?\N- How confident do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.94,0:12:13.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to the absence of Mac...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.11,0:12:14.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I now have great\Nhopes of winning the title.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.74,0:12:16.47,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Black Eagle?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:18.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never even heard of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.58,0:12:20.64,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So it may safely be said that I will\Nbe the one to win the championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.19,0:12:28.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:34.13,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Mac!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.53,0:12:41.50,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So you are going to participate\Nin the race after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:44.00,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is the prototype of\Nmy missing engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.67,0:12:47.27,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I had kept it at a friend's place,\Nso it wasn't destroyed in the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:50.81,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be not as powerful as\Nthe other one, but I'll race with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:53.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck to you, Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:57.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do what little I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.39,0:13:00.32,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:02.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:24.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:28.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really a fine day for flying,\Nisn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:31.11,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Has Moriarty appeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.75,0:13:32.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:49.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take care of Mrs. Hudson.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fly with Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:52.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:07.48,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, the moment has come\Nfor me to show the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.45,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,that my "Crow" is Number One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.09,0:14:12.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:35.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to see who's going\Nto win the championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.62,0:14:43.99,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, Mrs. Hudson?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:44.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.13,0:14:54.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How strange!\NHe still hasn't appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.17,0:14:57.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It fell apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:03.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my god!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:10.17,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Moriarty's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:16.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.76,0:15:22.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.53,0:15:24.12,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:26.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.62,0:15:46.14,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.42,0:15:53.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fantastic engine\NI have stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.43,0:15:55.19,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It works perfectly with\Nmy beloved 'Crow'!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.73,0:15:56.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Dirty rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:58.76,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:02.70,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You, get out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:16.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How paltry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:19.08,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:23.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.07,0:16:34.62,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:38.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:50.74,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm coming apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.45,0:16:53.65,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that we're\Nthe last two planes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:54.82,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:55.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.79,0:16:58.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to technique,\NI can hold my own against anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:12.10,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.61,0:17:16.78,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,How swift he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:18.44,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's how you're going to be,\NI'll just come to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:34.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,All right then, commence\NMrs. Hudson's basket operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.34,0:17:43.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like some tea?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.21,0:17:47.87,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,And, here's some dessert as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.61,0:17:53.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.31,0:17:53.94,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.79,0:18:02.22,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out! Right, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:07.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.00,0:18:10.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.97,0:18:12.93,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.47,0:18:14.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.27,0:18:21.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:29.24,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.32,0:18:30.34,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:34.68,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:51.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:57.57,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:18:59.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Moriarty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.15,0:19:03.88,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,So Holmes, we finally make\Nthe time for our final confrontation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:05.58,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I will settle my accounts\Nwith you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.42,0:19:07.15,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:10.21,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Just look!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:15.02,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:19.43,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.72,0:19:37.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit, Mac Bain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.35,0:19:41.29,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:49.96,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry that your engine is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.03,0:19:50.72,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:52.06,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I can always make a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:54.80,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather lose my engine than\Nseeing it misused by a villain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:57.40,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.90,0:19:58.77,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:05.30,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I do this and this, and then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:11.25,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor, here we come!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:19.16,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:22.53,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.53,0:20:25.86,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:30.73,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,He has the devil's luck, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.17,0:20:32.54,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:46.38,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Two planes are leading.\NMac's and Hudson's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:09.66,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.06,0:21:29.03,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.43,0:21:30.09,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Helen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.01,0:21:48.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Congratulations\Non your victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.28,0:21:51.05,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Mac.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:52.28,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.82,0:21:54.98,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe my victory entirely\Nto your kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.59,0:21:58.49,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's due to your\Nexcellent engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.06,0:22:02.26,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps to\NMrs. Hudson's lunch basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.50,0:22:04.46,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that may be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.37,0:22:12.50,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,I wished I could have asked Professor\NMoriarty how he liked the dessert.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.57,0:22:15.63,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet it was the bitterest\Ncake he had ever tasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:19.41,Text,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.98,0:22:22.97,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we raise our glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.58,0:22:25.57,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.85,0:22:26.68,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.09,0:22:29.61,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,we completely blew it, didn't we?
