Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.57,0:23:47.53,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Producers\NSATOSHI FUJII, REIKO MATSUO\N& JONATHAN KLEIN
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.60,0:23:49.57,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Subtitlers\NBRETT JACOBSEN, DIANA TOLIN,\NAKI MATSUMOTO & MAKOTO SHIRAI
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.48,0:24:00.57,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Moriarty's mechanical dragon attacks\Na speeding locomotive...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.81,0:24:03.94,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,and they steal a parrot that\Nbelongs to one of the passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.35,0:24:07.34,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, Holmes finds out\Nthat there's a relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.42,0:24:09.45,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,between the parrot and Indian\Nmerchant who's gone missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.82,0:24:12.19,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,What will the parrot tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.96,0:24:17.36,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find yourself in a mystery,\Nplease come see us at Baker Street.
